title: Chris Brown - exclusiv
description: Exclusive is the second studio album by pop/R&B singer Chris Brown. The album was originally going to be titled Graduation, but was renamed due to rapper Kanye West&#039;s album going by the same name. The album was originally scheduled to be released August 28, 2007, but was pushed back to October 30, 2007, then pushed back even further to its final release date of November 6, 2007.[1] This album was #34 on Rolling Stone&#039;s list of the Top 50 Albums of 2007.[2]
